        scanned copy to <a href="javascript:void(0);">info@mitrsewa.in</a> cc to <a
        href="javascript:void(0);">zubair.alam@mitrsewa.in</a>; and b) delivering the physical
        copy by post / hand.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 4%;"><b>For Mitr Sewa Private Limited</b></p>

